Package seedu.address.logic.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    Adds a person to the address book.
    AddCommandIntegrationTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model) for AddCommand.
    AddCommandTest  
    ClearCommand
    Clears the address book.
    ClearCommandTest  
    Command
    Represents a command with hidden internal logic and the ability to be executed.
    CommandResult
    Represents the result of a command execution.
    CommandTestUtil
    Contains helper methods for testing commands.
    DeleteCommand
    Deletes a person identified using it's displayed index from the address book.
    DeleteCommandTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model, UndoCommand and RedoCommand) and unit tests for DeleteCommand.
    EditCommand
    Edits the details of an existing person in the address book.
    EditCommand.EditPersonDescriptor
    Stores the details to edit the person with.
    EditCommandTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model, UndoCommand and RedoCommand) and unit tests for EditCommand.
    EditPersonDescriptorTest  
    ExitCommand
    Terminates the program.
    ExitCommandTest  
    FindCommand
    Finds and lists all persons in address book whose name contains any of the argument keywords.
    FindCommandTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model) for FindCommand.
    HelpCommand
    Format full help instructions for every command for display.
    HelpCommandTest  
    HistoryCommand
    Lists all the commands entered by user from the start of app launch.
    HistoryCommandTest  
    ListCommand
    Lists all persons in the address book to the user.
    ListCommandTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model) and unit tests for ListCommand.
    RedoCommand
    Reverts the model's address book to its previously undone state.
    RedoCommandTest  
    SelectCommand
    Selects a person identified using it's displayed index from the address book.
    SelectCommandTest
    Contains integration tests (interaction with the Model) for SelectCommand.
    UndoCommand
    Reverts the model's address book to its previous state.
    UndoCommandTest
